# /new-component <name>

Before any other action, read `AGENTS.md`, `.aem/context/components.json`, `.aem/context/conventions.md`, and `ui.apps/AGENTS.md`. Honor every rule under the **Agentic workflow guardrails** sections.

## Flow

1. Confirm `<name>` does not already exist in `.aem/context/components.json`.
2. Delegate to the `aem-component-author` subagent (project-scoped, installed in `.claude/agents/`).
3. After the subagent completes, run `{{MVN_CMD}} -pl ui.apps -PautoInstallPackage clean install` and report the outcome.
4. Confirm the new component now appears in `.aem/context/components.json` with an updated marker checksum.

Stop if any guardrail would be violated.
